        protected final ArrayList<M extends BaseMergeSource<M>> finishedSources
        For bookkeeping only. Unused. Once the entire contents of a source has been written to the target, the source is placed in here and removed from sources.

      • processTop

        protected abstract void processTop()
                            throws IOException
        Processes the top of the MergeSource stack. If any of the merge sources is finished then that it should be removed from the sources list and placed in the finishedSources list.

        Pre-condition

        • sources is sorted
          • sources has at least 2 elements

        Post-condition

        • sources is sorted
          • sources contains no finished instances.
        Throws:
        IOException
